name: comfyui-rmbg
description: Remove image backgrounds and return transparent PNG cutouts. Use for 抠图, 去背景, remove background, transparent background, RMBG/rembg, alpha matte, foreground extraction, product/character cutouts, or Photoshop-like magic wand requests that should only remove edge-connected same-color regions. Also covers smart matting for AI-generated assets — trigger words 智能抠图, AI生图抠图, smart matte, ERMBG — which auto-routes per image (saturated bg → chromatic key, white/black → luminance key, clean RGBA → passthrough, dirty RGBA → re-matte) and is the right choice when the input came out of an AI generator (Flux, SDXL, Qwen-Edit, GPT-Image, etc.) or already has a dirty alpha channel that needs re-matting.
